GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Differentiators> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Differentiators> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Differentiators> ;
    narr:childCount "42"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "9cecc1fa54e811e4d98f2db09af3cfa87c3e4e84" ;
    narr:narration """This hub gathers what makes aswritten distinct from generic AI, spanning enterprise infrastructure, epistemological architecture, and demo-form claims. The oldest and most-cited enterprise hook is [cross-repo, cross-platform, org-owned memory](narr:Narrative_CrossRepoMemoryEnterpriseHook), grounded in the customer's chief architect's Mar-2026 articulation that [Copilot Memories is scoped to a repo](narr:Obs_CustomerArchitectCrossRepoQuote) while the enterprise customer's code spans BitBucket, GitHub Enterprise, and customer-owned repos. A second pillar, sharpened by Scarlet in Apr-2026, is the [citation-engine-not-synthesis moat](narr:Narrative_CitationEngineNotSynthesis): aswritten expands from sources to citations rather than compressing to platitude, with [agents citing which memories shaped them](narr:Obs_AgentsCiteMemories) as the visible proof of influence. A third cluster is composability: [module layering via multi-repo compilation](narr:Narrative_ModuleLayeringComposability), [living auto-updating modules vs. static books](narr:Narrative_LivingEvolvingModules), and [knowledge packaging as a second moment of value](narr:Narrative_KnowledgePackagingMoment). The Jul-2026 David Nolen session added two new differentiator forms: [storing the decision process, not the half-baked artifact](narr:Narrative_StoreDecisionProcessNotArtifact), and [decision-archaeology as the strongest demo form](narr:Narrative_MoneyAnswerDecisionArchaeology) — the 'how did we end up here' query that David constructed unprompted, reaching for his DRW Confluence trauma as the [emotional peak of the demo](narr:Narrative_ArchaeologyQueryUseCase). A parallel from a design collaborator independently arrived at the same architecture: [design-token extraction as structurally identical to perspective extraction](narr:Narrative_DesignTokenPerspectiveParallel). Further differentiators include [introspect surfacing 62 gaps in nine days](narr:Narrative_ProductSurfacesOwnRoadmap), [worldview encoding of AI behavior criticisms](narr:Position_WorldviewEncodesAIBehavior), [undocumented-knowledge extraction](narr:Obs_UndocumentedKnowledgeQuote), and [style/voice encoding for one-shot drafts](narr:Obs_StyleVoiceEncoding). The GitHub-infrastructure analogy and shared-agent-memory concept sit at the relational edge.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ArchaeologyQueryUseCase> ;
